<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink324">
<l>erikavarn tuṇṭa veṉṟūḻ nīḷiṭaic</l>
<l>ciṟitukaṇ paṭuppiṉuṅ kāṇkuveṉ maṉṟa</l>
<l>naḷḷeṉ kaṅku ṉaḷimaṉai neṭunakar</l>
<l>vēṅkai veṉṟa cuṇaṅkiṟ</l>
<l>ṟēmpāy kūntaṉ māa yōḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>If I sleep for a little bit in this long sun-drenched path, </l>
<l>that has been seized and eaten by fire, I will see the dark girl </l>
<l>with her hair spreading fragrance </l>
<l>and beauty spots [on her skin]  surpassing Kino tree flowers </l>
<l>in the large city, where [her] large house [stands] in full darkness. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
